          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Load Chapter 5 Scene 7</li>
            <li>Pick the first option with Mr. Gap then pick "it's me!" when prompted <span class="text-yellow-400">(Thanks to Ash from the Homicipher server for letting me know about the update!)</span></li>
            <li>Break the mirror and go to the right, then forward.</li>
            <li>When prompted with a bar to write text in, write the wrong name.</li>
            <li>When you enter the room after the telephone and turn the corner, you meet Mr. Scarletella. Press on him instead of leaving. Attack him, then turn right</li>
            <li>Let the timer run out then attack him twice more.</li>
            <li>Faced with Mr. Scarletella standing in front of you, pick: first option, second option, second option, first option, first option, first option.</li>
            <li>Pick "break" within the time limit.</li>
            <li>When you see his red umbrella, pick "Break"</li>
            <li>When prompted, choose "I defeated it".</li>
