        <div class="prose prose-invert mb-8">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-400 mb-4">Goodbye End</h4>
          
          <div class="bg-red-900 bg-opacity-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
            <p class="font-bold">IMPORTANT NOTE: Make sure you have already completed the Scarlet Rain End.</p>
          </div>

          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Load Chapter 5 Scene 24 and choose to run.</li>
            <li>When prompted with two options in the mirror room, choose to run again <span class="text-gray-400">(going back would prompt you to the scene with Mr. Scarletella and you will have to do everything again)</span>.</li>
            <li>Talk to the telephone and pick the second option.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-invert mb-8">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-400 mb-4">Awakening End</h4>
          
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Load Chapter 5 Scene 25 and choose to break the umbrella.</li>
            <li>You'll be asked to make a choice of either a smartphone or a telephone.</li>
          </ol>

          <div class="bg-yellow-900 bg-opacity-50 p-4 rounded-lg my-4">
            <p>💾 It is recommended to save here since this is where the endings will branch.</p>
            <p class="mt-2">If you pick the smartphone then you will achieve the Awakening End.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-invert">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-400 mb-4">Tranquil End</h4>
          
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Load Chapter 5 Scene 25 and choose to break the umbrella.</li>
            <li>You'll be asked to make a choice of either a smartphone or a telephone.</li>
          </ol>

