            <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
              <li>If you choose "I defeated it", then it will lead to the Victory End.</li>
              <li>If you choose "I was dreaming", then it will lead to the Tranquil End.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
